name: Los Suaves Negroes - lounge & bossa Turbonegro tribute [CD]
description:
There is no other band out there more kitsch than Turbonegro and therefor we have compiled this pink lounge compilation where various artists have contributed with their own unique interpretations of classic Turbonegro songs under the flag of lounge/bossanova. With titles like “I Got Erection”, “Denim Demon” and “Sailor Man”, we have an album filled with beautiful evil art. Turbonegro was founded in Oslo/Norway in the late 80’s. Since then they have released four albums, toured massively (even sold out the House Of Blues in Los Angeles two days in a row in December 2004) and some people even call them “the worlds biggest underground rockband”.
